            <title>[SOLR-6987] SSL support for MiniSolrCloudCluster</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6987</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3854&quot; title=&quot;SolrCloud does not work with https&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-3854&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-3854&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; added SSL support, but didn&apos;t add support to the MiniSolrCloudCluster.  The existing TestMiniSolrCloudCluster doesn&apos;t inherit from SolrTestCaseJ4, so the test never failed or required SuppressSSL.&lt;/p&gt;

